  ('Trends','129577','Sabian Lunch Cooler Bag','sabian-lunch-cooler-bag-129577','Bags','Cooler Bags','Medium-sized 8L lunch cooler bag made from natural jute and designed for everyday use. Features a Metpet insulated lining to keep your lunch and snacks cool on the go. Natural cotton handles make it easy to carry while a front slip pocket provides convenient extra storage. Perfect for work, school, or any outing.','Add your logo to the Sabian Lunch Cooler Bag with screen print per colour or colourflex transfer — medium-sized 8L lunch cooler bag made from natural jute and designed for everyday use. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "#D9CBB2", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
