  ('Trends','129578','Aden Lunch Cooler Bag','aden-lunch-cooler-bag-129578','Bags','Cooler Bags','A 9.5L cotton cooler bag, designed for simple, everyday food and drink storage on the go. The insulated Metpet lining helps maintain temperature for longer, perfect for packed lunches, picnics and short outings. Natural cotton carry handles provide a comfortable grip, while the front slip pocket offers convenient extra storage and a practical branding area.','Brand the the Aden Lunch Cooler Bag with screen print per colour or colourflex transfer — a 9.5L cotton cooler bag, designed for simple, everyday food and drink storage on the go. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "#D9CBB2", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
