  ('Trends','129615','Cora Coffee Mug','cora-coffee-mug-129615','Drinkware','Mugs','An attractive 355ml ceramic mug, designed for everyday use with a clean and modern profile. Perfectly suited to full colour, wraparound branding, it features a glossy, white glazed outer with a contrasting glazed inner for a durable yet refined finish. Presented in an individual natural gift box. This product is not dishwasher safe and handwashing is recommended.','Put your logo on the Cora Coffee Mug with sublimation print — an attractive 355ml ceramic mug, designed for everyday use with a clean and modern profile. From 36 units.',36,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": ""}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "#F5D400", "image": ""}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "#F26722", "image": ""}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "#C8102E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Bright Green", "hex": "#66BB2E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Teal", "hex": "#008C8C", "image": ""}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "#7DD3FC", "image": ""}, {"name": "Dark Blue", "hex": "#12294A", "image": ""}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
