  ('Trends','129665','Corsica Coffee Cup','corsica-coffee-cup-129665','Drinkware','Coffee Cups','The Corsica Coffee Cup is a 350ml double wall coffee cup with a clean, modern profile designed for everyday use. It features a sturdy stainless steel outer with a polypropylene inner, providing durability alongside practical insulation. The flip closure lid folds all the way back for easy drinking while the smooth, painted finish is available in a range of great colours to suit your brand. The colour match lid and cup completes the look for a consistent, considered appearance. Presented in a natural gift box.','Add your logo to the Corsica Coffee Cup with pad print per colour/position or screen print — the Corsica Coffee Cup is a 350ml double wall coffee cup with a clean, modern profile designed for everyday use. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": ""}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "#F5D400", "image": ""}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "#F26722", "image": ""}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "#E85D9E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "#C8102E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Bright Green", "hex": "#66BB2E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Dark Green", "hex": "#14532D", "image": ""}, {"name": "Teal", "hex": "#008C8C", "image": ""}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "#7DD3FC", "image": ""}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "#1D4ED8", "image": ""}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "#1B2A4A", "image": ""}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "#6B21A8", "image": ""}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
