  ('Trends','129697','Barista Stackable Coffee Mug','barista-stackable-coffee-mug-129697','Drinkware','Mugs','This 300ml ceramic coffee mug features a space saving stackable design, perfect for efficient storage in kitchens or workspaces. The matte glazed outer with gloss inner and rim, along with a fluted bottom section creates a clean, modern contrast of finishes. Designed for everyday use, it combines practicality with a refined aesthetic. Presented in a natural gift box. This product is not dishwasher safe and handwashing is recommended.','Brand the the Barista Stackable Coffee Mug with pad print per colour/position — this 300ml ceramic coffee mug features a space saving stackable design, perfect for efficient storage in kitchens or workspaces. From 36 units.',36,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Ecru", "hex": "#D9CBB2", "image": ""}, {"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": ""}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "#C8102E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "#1D4ED8", "image": ""}, {"name": "Dark Grey", "hex": "#4B4B4B", "image": ""}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
