  ('Trends','129704','Pulse Sports Cap','pulse-sports-cap-129704','Headwear','Caps','A lightweight sports cap, made from 100% nylon taslan, offering a clean, versatile look for any activity. Side mesh panels and sewn eyelets provide effective ventilation while the adjustable back strap ensures a secure, comfortable fit. Designed for regular wear for workdays, events, and sport, it combines practical performance with everyday style.','Put your logo on the Pulse Sports Cap with colourflex transfer or faux embroidery — a lightweight sports cap, made from 100% nylon taslan, offering a clean, versatile look for any activity. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
