  ('Trends','129689','SPICE Waste2Gear Umbrella','spice-waste2gear-umbrella-129689','Outdoor & Sports','Umbrellas','This classy umbrella is made from recycled ocean nylon and features a 59cm eight panel canopy designed for reliable wet weather protection. Fibreglass ribs and shaft provide strength and flexibility, while rounded ABS tips enhance safety and durability. The cork handle adds a natural, comfortable grip and creates a strong visual contrast against the canopy for a distinctive, premium finish. It is 100% carbon neutral to delivery.','Add your logo to the SPICE Waste2Gear Umbrella with screen print per position — this classy umbrella is made from recycled ocean nylon and features a 59cm eight panel canopy designed for reliable wet weather protection. From 10 units.',10,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
