  ('Trends','129698','Baseline Pickleball Set','baseline-pickleball-set-129698','Outdoor & Sports','Sports Products','Pickleball is one of the fastest growing recreational sports and this convenient set makes it easy to get started. It includes two fibreglass paddles and two pickleballs, neatly packed in a zippered carry bag for practical transport and storage. The lightweight and durable paddles feature non-slip EVA taped grips, making them ideal for beginners, casual and recreational players.','Brand the the Baseline Pickleball Set with faux embroidery or screen print per colour — pickleball is one of the fastest growing recreational sports and this convenient set makes it easy to get started. From 8 units.',8,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
