  ('Trends','129699','Neoprene Cup Sleeve - Small','neoprene-cup-sleeve-small-129699','Barware & Accessories','Stubby Holders','A 3mm neoprene insulating cup sleeve designed for takeaway and reusable cups. It helps maintain drink temperature for longer while providing a comfortable grip when holding hot or cold beverages. The simple, lightweight design makes it easy to use on the go, and it is well suited to daily coffee runs and reusable cup use. Durable sublimation print delivers a vibrant, high-quality finish for strong branding impact. A production lead time of 25 working days applies via air freight.','Personalise the the Neoprene Cup Sleeve - Small with sublimation print — a 3mm neoprene insulating cup sleeve designed for takeaway and reusable cups. From 50 units.',50,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
