  ('Trends','129700','Neoprene Cup Sleeve - Medium','neoprene-cup-sleeve-medium-129700','Barware & Accessories','Stubby Holders','A 3mm neoprene insulating cup sleeve designed for medium sized takeaway and reusable cups. It helps maintain drink temperature for longer while providing a comfortable grip when holding hot or cold beverages, making it ideal for everything from morning coffee runs to iced coffees on the go. The simple, lightweight design ensures easy everyday use. Durable sublimation print delivers a vibrant, high-quality finish for strong branding impact. A production lead time of 25 working days applies via air freight.','Put your logo on the Neoprene Cup Sleeve - Medium with sublimation print — a 3mm neoprene insulating cup sleeve designed for medium sized takeaway and reusable cups. From 50 units.',50,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
