  ('Trends','129702','PVC Key Covers','pvc-key-covers-129702','Giveaways & Event Accessories','Novelty Giveaways','A custom moulded PVC key cover designed for bold, detailed branding. It includes up to four colours on both sides, with additional colours available at extra cost, and can be produced in sizes up to 50mm x 50mm. Durable PVC construction helps protect keys while adding a distinctive, tactile element. The silver ball chain makes it easy to attach to keyrings or bags, and it is supplied with a full colour backing card for an enhanced presentation. A production lead time of 25 working days applies via air freight.','Add your logo to the PVC Key Covers with moulded up to 4 colours or additional moulded colours per colour/design — a custom moulded PVC key cover designed for bold, detailed branding. From 250 units.',250,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
