  ('Trends','129723','Terry Towelling Bucket Hat with Full Colour Patch','terry-towelling-bucket-hat-with-full-colour-patch-129723','Headwear','Bucket Hats','A comfortable terry towelling bucket hat lined with poplin material, designed for a soft, textured finish. It features a full colour sublimation patch on the front, available in round, square or rectangular shapes, finished with satin stitched edges for a clean, detailed look. Available in three sizes to fit most people, including kids. The fabric complies with AS/NZS sun protection standards. A production lead time of 35 working days applies via air freight.','Put your logo on the Terry Towelling Bucket Hat with Full Colour Patch with sublimation print or full colour patch — a comfortable terry towelling bucket hat lined with poplin material, designed for a soft, textured finish. From 100 units.',100,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
