  ('Trends','129725','Cabana Custom Wide Brim Hat','cabana-custom-wide-brim-hat-129725','Headwear','Wide Brim Hats','A wide brim hat made from woven polyester, designed for lightweight comfort and sun protection. It features full colour custom print for high impact branding, along with an inner lining for added comfort during extended wear. The adjustable woven chin strap includes a safety breakaway clip for secure, practical use outdoors. Available in three sizes to fit most people, including kids. The fabric complies with AS/NZS sun protection standards. A production lead time of 35 working days applies via air freight.','Brand the the Cabana Custom Wide Brim Hat with sublimation print — a wide brim hat made from woven polyester, designed for lightweight comfort and sun protection. From 100 units.',100,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
