  ('Trends','129726','Custom Cozy Socks','custom-cozy-socks-129726','Apparel','Socks','Custom knitted socks designed for serious warmth and comfort, featuring a soft shearling lining for a cosy feel. The non-slip grip on the sole provides added traction and support on indoor surfaces, making them ideal for relaxed home wear. Available in two sizes for a comfortable fit across most wearers, and up to four knit colours for customised styling. A production lead time of 30 working days applies via air freight.','Personalise the the Custom Cozy Socks with knitted up to four colours — custom knitted socks designed for serious warmth and comfort, featuring a soft shearling lining for a cosy feel. From 100 units.',100,true,null,'supplier','{"sizes": ["Medium", "Large"], "rows": [{"label": "Ankle Height cm", "values": ["15", "18"]}, {"label": "Foot Length cm", "values": ["23", "25"]}]}'::jsonb,null,'indent_air',null);
