  ('Trends','129735','Frontier Torrent Camping Blanket','frontier-torrent-camping-blanket-129735','Outdoor & Sports','Blankets','A lightweight, water-resistant blanket designed for comfort and practicality in any setting, whether camping, picnicking or relaxing outdoors. The included metal pegs help keep it securely in place during windy conditions or on uneven ground. When not in use, it folds neatly into a compact drawstring pouch for easy storage and transport. A zippered corner pocket keeps small essentials secure and offers a practical branding area. Presented with a Frontier branded hangtag.','Put your logo on the Frontier Torrent Camping Blanket with colourflex transfer or faux embroidery — a lightweight, water-resistant blanket designed for comfort and practicality in any setting, whether camping, picnicking or relaxing outdoors. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
