  ('Trends','133562','Cruise Custom Cap with Full Colour Patch','cruise-custom-cap-with-full-colour-patch-133562','Headwear','Caps','A 5-panel trucker hat designed for breathable comfort and everyday wear. It features mesh rear panels for improved airflow, a padded polyester front panel and pre-curved peak for a structured, modern fit. The front panel and patch both support full colour branding, and the patch is available in three shape options. An adjustable snapback closure and integrated sweatband provide a secure and comfortable fit. A production lead time of 35 working days applies via air freight.','Brand the the Cruise Custom Cap with Full Colour Patch with full colour patch or sublimation print — a 5-panel trucker hat designed for breathable comfort and everyday wear. From 100 units.',100,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
