  ('Trends','133563','Falcon Custom Cap with Full Colour Patch','falcon-custom-cap-with-full-colour-patch-133563','Headwear','Caps','A fully customisable 6-panel cap made from polyester, designed for a clean, structured look and everyday wear. It features a pre-curved peak for a classic fit, along with a full colour sublimation patch available in three shape options. The adjustable snapback closure ensures a secure and comfortable fit. A production lead time of 35 working days applies via air freight.','Personalise the the Falcon Custom Cap with Full Colour Patch with sublimation print or rectangle patch - 70mm x 50mm | square patch - 50mm x 50mm | round patch - 50mm circle — a fully customisable 6-panel cap made from polyester, designed for a clean, structured look and everyday wear. From 100 unit',100,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
