  ('Trends','133807','Kadi Carry-On Suitcase - Business','kadi-carry-on-suitcase-business-133807','Bags','Travel & Duffle Bags','A compact 38L hard shell suitcase combining a sleek aesthetic with practical functionality. Scratch resistant, 100% German polycarbonate keeps it lightweight, yet durable for frequent use. An integrated laptop pocket and quick-access front compartment provide convenient storage for your tech, while five internal compartments support efficient packing. Finished with a multi-stop telescopic handle, 360-degree silent wheels, waterproof zippers and an integrated TSA lock, it ensures smooth, secure and effortless travel.','Personalise the the Kadi Carry-On Suitcase - Business with prism digital print per position — a compact 38L hard shell suitcase combining a sleek aesthetic with practical functionality. From 1 unit.',1,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "#36454F", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,'indent_air',null);
