  ('Trends','133808','Kadi Carry-On Suitcase - Leisure','kadi-carry-on-suitcase-leisure-133808','Bags','Travel & Duffle Bags','A sleek and compact hard shell suitcase with a standard capacity of 37L and is expandable to 41L for additional packing space. Crafted from scratch resistant 100% German polycarbonate, it is lightweight, yet durable for frequent use. Internal reinforcement adds extra strength and durability, while zipped compartments, sealed pockets and a laundry bag allow for efficient packing. Finished with a multi-stop telescopic handle, 360-degree silent wheels, waterproof zippers and an integrated TSA lock, it ensures smooth, secure and effortless travel.','Put your logo on the Kadi Carry-On Suitcase - Leisure with prism digital print per position — a sleek and compact hard shell suitcase with a standard capacity of 37L and is expandable to 41L for additional packing space. From 1 unit.',1,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Pebble", "hex": "#B8AE9C", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,'indent_air',null);
