  ('Trends','133809','Kadi Check-In Suitcase - Medium','kadi-check-in-suitcase-medium-133809','Bags','Travel & Duffle Bags','A spacious expandable hard shell check-in suitcase with a capacity of 78L and is expandable to 84L for additional packing space when needed. Crafted from scratch resistant 100% German polycarbonate, it combines lightweight performance with the durability required for frequent travel. Thoughtful internal organisation and a separate laundry bag help keep packing streamlined and simple, while the multi-stop telescopic handle and easy spin, 360-degree silent wheels deliver smooth maneuverability. Finished with waterproof zippers and an integrated TSA lock for secure, reliable and easy travel.','Add your logo to the Kadi Check-In Suitcase - Medium with prism digital print per position — a spacious expandable hard shell check-in suitcase with a capacity of 78L and is expandable to 84L for additional packing space when needed. From 1 unit.',1,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "#36454F", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,'indent_air',null);
