  ('Trends','133811','Skullcandy Icon 180 Wireless Headphones','skullcandy-icon-180-wireless-headphones-133811','Technology','Earbuds & Headphones','The Icon 180 delivers reliable everyday performance with Skullcandy''s signature focus on comfort, durability and simplicity. It features up to 50-hours battery life, with Rapid Charge delivering up to 4 hours of playback from a 10-minute charge. Bluetooth v5.3 with Google Fast Pair ensures quick, stable connectivity and a Clear Voice smart microphone supports clearer call audio. Customise your listening with preset EQ modes or in-app tuning with the 5-band EQ. Built for daily use, with a clean, comfortable on-ear design. Please note the branding on the packaging is subject to change without notice, and this product cannot be supplied unbranded or without the Skullcandy branding.','Personalise the the Skullcandy Icon 180 Wireless Headphones with pad print - both ear pieces or pad print per colour — the Icon 180 delivers reliable everyday performance with Skullcandy''s signature focus on comfort, durability and simplicity. From 2 units.',2,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
