  ('Trends','133812','HangFindy Bluetooth Tracker','hangfindy-bluetooth-tracker-133812','Technology','Tech Accessories','A Bluetooth tracker designed for everyday peace of mind, compatible with iOS and Android devices. It connects via Apple Find My or Google Find My Device networks for crowdsourced tracking without GPS or Wi-Fi. The premium PU finish delivers a refined, fashion-led design suited to bags, keys, luggage and accessories, combining practical tracking functionality with a clean, modern aesthetic. A built-in sound alert helps locate nearby items, while the loop attachment and replaceable battery add everyday practicality. Presented in a black gift box with product branding.','Put your logo on the HangFindy Bluetooth Tracker with laser engraving or pad print per colour — a Bluetooth tracker designed for everyday peace of mind, compatible with iOS and Android devices. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": ""}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
