  ('Trends','133813','Bodum Brazil French Press 1L','bodum-brazil-french-press-1l-133813','Home & Living','Kitchen & Dining','An iconic 1L French press coffee maker designed to deliver full flavour and aroma with every brew. The borosilicate glass carafe preserves the coffee''s natural flavour while the BPA-free plastic frame, handle and lid are lightweight and finished with Bodum branding at the base. A stainless steel plunger and filter system helps prevent grounds escaping when pouring. A more environmentally friendly brewing method requiring no paper filters or plastic capsules. Presented in a printed Bodum branded gift box.','Add your logo to the Bodum Brazil French Press 1L with pad print per colour or imitation etch — an iconic 1L French press coffee maker designed to deliver full flavour and aroma with every brew. From 6 units.',6,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
