  ('Trends','133814','Bodum Brazil French Press 350ml','bodum-brazil-french-press-350ml-133814','Home & Living','Kitchen & Dining','An iconic 350ml French press coffee maker designed for individual use, delivering full flavour and aroma with every brew. The borosilicate glass carafe preserves the coffee''s natural flavour, while the BPA-free plastic frame, handle and lid are lightweight and finished with Bodum branding at the base. The stainless steel plunger and filter system helps prevent grounds escaping during pouring. A more environmentally friendly brewing method requiring no paper filters or plastic capsules. Presented in a printed Bodum branded gift box.','Brand the the Bodum Brazil French Press 350ml with imitation etch or pad print per colour — an iconic 350ml French press coffee maker designed for individual use, delivering full flavour and aroma with every brew. From 6 units.',6,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
