  ('Trends','133815','Bodum Assam Tea Press','bodum-assam-tea-press-133815','Drinkware','Teaware','An innovative 500ml glass teapot with infuser, designed for controlled brewing and a clean, refreshing taste. Made from heat-resistant borosilicate glass, it features a silicone filter rim and plastic handle for practical everyday use. The patented system stops the brewing process after plunging to help prevent over-extraction, while the stainless steel plunger ensures smooth operation. Presented in a printed Bodum branded gift box.','Personalise the the Bodum Assam Tea Press with imitation etch or pad print per colour — an innovative 500ml glass teapot with infuser, designed for controlled brewing and a clean, refreshing taste. From 6 units.',6,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "#000000", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
