  ('Trends','133817','Bodum Bistro Double Wall Mugs - Set of 2','bodum-bistro-double-wall-mugs-set-of-2-133817','Drinkware','Glassware','A stylish set of two 300ml double wall espresso mugs designed for your morning coffee hit. Made from mouth-blown, heat-resistant borosilicate glass, the double wall construction maintains beverage temperature while ensuring the mug remain comfortable to hold. Lightweight and smooth to the touch, each cup fits neatly in the hand is suitable for espresso as well as small, chilled desserts. Presented in a printed Bodum branded gift box.','Add your logo to the Bodum Bistro Double Wall Mugs - Set of 2 with imitation etch per position (both glasses) or pad print per colour/position (both glasses) — a stylish set of two 300ml double wall espresso mugs designed for your morning coffee hit. From 6 units.',6,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Clear", "hex": "#EAF3F7", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,null);
